# ASFM
The official implementation of "Adaptive Spatial-Frequency Masking Consistency Learning for Semi-Supervised Medical Image Segmentation"

## Requirements
This repository is based on PyTorch 2.1.1, CUDA 12.1 and Python 3.9.21. 

Install the main packages:
```angular2html
pytorch == 2.1.1
torchvision == 0.16.1
cuda == 12.1
cudnn == 8.0
```
